column3: Have you submitted a contributor license agreement? If not, please follow the steps described at http://www.jetbrains.com/agreements/cla/ to sign it.
Actually I keep getting "Something is wrong. Please, try again later or reach out to us at ..."
Oh whoops, looks like it did work--I didn't realize it sent me docusign thing. Or rather it sent me one docusign thing for each time I clicked submit...I signed one of them.
We received the CLA, thank you.
